author: Marian Edelman
message: You're not obligated to win. You're obligated to keep trying to do the best you can every day.
title: Thought of the day

author: Byron Pulsifer
message: Everyone can taste success when the going is easy, but few know how to taste victory when times get tough.
title: Thought of the day

author: Sue Patton Thoele
message: Deep listening is miraculous for both listener and speaker.When someone receives us with open-hearted, non-judging, intensely interested listening, our spirits expand.
title: Thought of the day

author: Frank Crane
message: You may be deceived if you trust too much, but you will live in torment if you don't trust enough.
title: Thought of the day
